snippet: Angered by President Mohamed Morsi’s hurried effort to pass Egypt’s new constitution, tens of thousands of people streamed into Tahrir Square.

byline.contributor: David D. Kirkpatrick, Joe Gabra and Mayy El Sheikh contributed reporting.
